eplimited.osea.classification

Class Matcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • eplimited.osea.classification.Matcher

  • public class Matcher
extends java.lang.Object
    Match beats to previous beats. Matcher contains functions for managing template matching of beats and managing of feature data associated with each beat type. These functions are called functions in Classifier. Beats are matched to previoiusly detected beats types based on how well they match point by point in a MATCH_LENGTH region centered on FIDMARK (R-wave location).
